JOHANNESBURG - Songs are part of many political gatherings in South Africa, be they old struggle favourites or new tunes. EXPLAINER: DA to elect 'new' leadership Since the start of the DA's federal congress on Saturday morning,  eNCA has been battling to work out the lyrics and title of this song by the party's Western Cape leader Bonginkosi Madikizela. Can you name the 'struggle song" below? Tweet us @eNCA if you can. Hint: We have reason to believe this song is in Afrikaans. eNCA